GIVEAWAY: it’s #nationalreadabookday and we’re giving away a special Belaire swag bag! 

To enter, you must purchase @richforever’s new book: “The Perfect Day To Boss Up” and post on stories the proof of purchase tagging @officialbelaire and @richforever! 

Once you’ve posted, like and comment “boss up!” on this post. We will be capping entries at the end of the week!
